ed="T" n="0845c16"/><persName key="A012815">釋永安</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000036649"><placeName>眉州</placeName><placeName>洪雅</placeName></placeName>人也。身裁么麼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g726"/>，面色黧䵟，<lb
ed="T" n="0845c17"/>言音鄙惡，而識量寬舒，大抵不可貲也。<date from-iso="+0854-04-05" key="j20330722033101" to-iso="+0854-05-04"><name>大中</name><lb
ed="T" n="0845c18"/>八年三月</date>中，詣<placeName key="PL000000034805">成都</placeName>，云造謁府帥<persName key="A010596">白<roleName>公</roleName>敏<lb
ed="T" n="0845c19"/>中</persName>，請奏寺額。以其足<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>跋</sic><corr>跛</corr></choice><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1621"/>，肩輿而至。人皆未<lb
ed="T" n="0845c20"/>甞見其登圊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1786"/>而旋溺也，故時呼為<persName key="A012815">無漏師</persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0845c21"/><persName key="A012815">安</persName>置<placeName key="PL000000034692">聖壽寺</placeName>中且十日，<persName key="A010596">白<roleName>中令</roleName></persName>俾差僧五、<lb
ed="T" n="0845c22"/>六，晝夜互守之而伺察焉。內外飲食，亦略<lb
ed="T" n="0845c23"/>同常人，而無解衣去二行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1787"/>之意。詳其十辰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1589"/><lb
ed="T" n="0845c24"/>之積，便旋何所，畢不可知。司徒<persName key="A010596">白<roleName>公</roleName></persName>奏額<lb
ed="T" n="0845c25"/>到日，便辭歸<placeName key="PL000000036573">眉郡</placeName>。判官<persName key="A012816">盧求</persName>見之，謂為小沙<lb
ed="T" n="0845c26"/>彌耳，人云：「此<ref type="person" target="#A012815">師</ref>年已八十餘矣！」</p><p xml:id="pT50p0845c2701"><lb
ed="T" n="0845c27"/>系曰：<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>人謂<persName key="A012815">安<roleName>公</roleName></persName>為<persName key="A012815">無漏師</persName>者，非也。夫斷<lb
ed="T" n="0845c28"/>煩惱不復隨增<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1788"/>，故永無種習，乃稱之無漏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g432"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0845c29"/>今以飲食之餘，歸于九孔，<persName key="A012815">安<roleName>公</roleName></persName>止二竅不<pb ed="T" n="0846a" xml:id="T50.2061.0846a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0846a01"/>流耳。《瑜伽》云無「內逼惱分」也<ptr target="#n1900"/>。然其位次、忍住<ptr type="glossary" target="#g164"/><lb
ed="T" n="0846a02"/>難知，啜茹如常，何緣不流二竅？觀夫《對法<lb
ed="T" n="0846a03"/>論》<ptr target="#n61"/>中有「清淨依止住食」、「示現依止住食」二種<ptr target="#n2731"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0846a04"/>則羅漢、菩薩、佛也。若然者，<persName key="A012815">安<roleName>公</roleName></persName>是示現依止<lb
ed="T" n="0846a05"/>住食──雖食不食，滓穢奚生？必也正名，以召<lb
ed="T" n="0846a06"/>其體<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1601"/>哉。</p>
